If, on the contrary, multiple internal reflections are considered (i.e., αd is small) the “complete” optical absorption coefficient – our αcomp(E) – will be given by65,71:6αcomp(E)=+1dln[(1−R)22T+(1−R)44T2+R2].\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
